{"about_the_game":"Take to the stars as the commander of the space station Alexandria IV, a place full of danger and strife, be it caused by mercenary aliens or power-hungry corporations. When an ancient secret is revealed on system Groombridge 34, the commander must act with strategy and diplomacy to avoid rupture between factions. In the future, we are not alone. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1699900/extras/alexgif.gif?t=1729108303\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Experience in first hand a new entry of the multi-media spanning series Veil of Truth, by award-winning author J.M. Beraldo.</strong><br><br></li><li><strong>Immerse yourself in a story-rich space opera as the commander of an entire space station. How will you deal with the myriad of problems life in space has to offer?</strong><br><br></li><li><strong>Fall in love with a diverse cast of characters, ranging from fellow humans to the strangest alien species. But beware! Romance between crew members is prohibited and has consequences...</strong><br><br></li><li><strong>Intergalactic trouble never ends: Prove yourself worthy of command by solving conflicts strategically in this five act episodic visual novel inspired by classics such as Deep Space 9 and Babylon 5.</strong></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Gaugamela","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1699900/2dc958b80300422a7870c31ea505e7cb9b7a6afe.jpg"},{"name":"Diplomactic Power","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1699900/2dc958b80300422a7870c31ea505e7cb9b7a6afe.jpg"},{"name":"Clarke's Fear","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1699900/2dc958b80300422a7870c31ea505e7cb9b7a6afe.jpg"},{"name":"We come in peace","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1699900/2dc958b80300422a7870c31ea505e7cb9b7a6afe.j